# AI coding-assistant context files — personal and per-developer: each collaborator may use a
# different assistant (or their own house style), so these never belong in the shared tree.
# CLAUDE.md was never committed; this keeps it (and the equivalents, incl. the .claude/ tool
# dir) untracked for everyone. The .githooks/pre-commit hook enforces the same list against
# an explicit `git add -f`.
CLAUDE.md
CLAUDE.local.md
**/CLAUDE.md
**/CLAUDE.local.md
.claude/
**/.claude/
GEMINI.md
**/GEMINI.md
.cursorrules
.windsurfrules
.aider*
.github/copilot-instructions.md

